    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it! It's been well-loved and runs like a dream. If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
