    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 naturally aspirated V8, delivering 414 hp with a soaring 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain is anchored by a variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the longevity of the high-strung internals. The chassis retains its composure via Electronic Damper Control (EDC), while the hydraulic steering rack provides the communicative feedback missing in modern EPS systems. Recent service includes a fresh fluid flush and Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires mounted on staggered Style 359 wheels. A mechanically robust driver\u2019s car for the purist seeking an analog experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
