    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a well-preserved example that offers a reliable and comfortable driving experience. The exterior paint remains vibrant and has been regularly waxed, showing only minor road-wear typical of a well-loved car. Inside, you\u2019ll find a smoke-free cabin with plush seating that shows minimal bolster wear and no rips or stains. All electronic features, including the climate control and infotainment system, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; it has a documented service history, a smooth-shifting transmission, and a responsive engine that starts perfectly every time. The tires have significant tread depth remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a solid, turn-key vehicle perfect for anyone seeking quality without the new-car price tag.",
