      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it's been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. It drives smoothly and is ready to hit the road for its next owner! If you're looking for a dependable ride that still looks great and feels even better behind the wheel, this is the one for you. Let\u2019s get you in for a test drive!",
