      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS system. Power is sent to the rear wheels through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term structural rigidity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the cooling system has been overhauled with an aluminum radiator. The suspension geometry remains sharp with upgraded polyurethane bushings. While the finish shows minor road-going patina consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals are robust, making this an ideal candidate for spirited canyon carving or track-day duty.",
